nexml.meta:
Both tables 3 and 5 (containing both matrices present in this paper) have been merged in one file, as table 5 shows phylogenetic characters for the five notothenioid families and table 3 shows characters for one of these families, the Channichthyidae family. The 26 first characters concerns notothenioid families and the following 17 characters only concerns the Channichthyidae family (characters coded with a question mark for the 4 other families). => 43 characters in all.
Added polymorphs. AB 10/18/12
